  <h2 id="privacy">Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    The ARCADIA appliance itself collects no telemetry, no analytics, and no
    conversation history. The only network traffic the unit ever generates
    is a daily software-update check that sends a per-unit license token over
    HTTPS and downloads signed update artifacts.
  </p>
  <p>
    The waitlist on this website stores: your lowercased email, the source
    page, an ISO timestamp, the two-letter country code your request came
    from, and a salted hash of your IP and User-Agent (used for abuse
    detection, not identification). It does not store your name, real IP,
    user-agent, referrer, or any tracking ID. There are no third-party
    trackers on this site.
  </p>
  <p>
    To request deletion of your waitlist entry, email
    <a href="mailto:hello@arcadiasurvival.com">hello@arcadiasurvival.com</a>.
  </p>

  <h2 id="oss">Open-source attribution</h2>
  <p>ARCADIA is built on the work of many open communities. Major components and licenses:</p>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Component</th><th>License</th><th>Project</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Wikipedia / Wikivoyage / Wikibooks</td><td>CC-BY-SA</td><td>Wikimedia Foundation</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Kiwix</td><td>GPL-3.0</td><td>Kiwix.org</td></tr>
      <tr><td>OpenStreetMap data</td><td>ODbL</td><td>OpenStreetMap contributors</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Photon geocoder</td><td>Apache-2.0</td><td>Komoot</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Argos Translate</td><td>MIT / CC-BY-SA</td><td>Argos Open Tech</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Piper TTS voices</td><td>MIT (per voice — see voices manifest)</td><td>Piper</td></tr>
      <tr><td>llama.cpp</td><td>MIT</td><td>ggerganov / contributors</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Astro</td><td>MIT</td><td>Astro</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p>
    Optional content packs (Kolibri Education Platform, Plants For A Future) carry their
    own licenses and are user-installed; ARCADIA does not redistribute them.
    Per-pack license details are shown when you install each pack on the unit.
  </p>

  <h2 id="warranty">Hardware warranty</h2>
  <p>
    Each ARCADIA unit ships with a one-year hardware warranty covering
    manufacturing defects in the appliance. Software updates and content
    refreshes are included for the life of the unit at no additional cost.
    Bundled accessories (EcoFlow River 3, foldable solar panel, hard-shell
    case, USB peripherals) are covered by their manufacturers' warranties;
    full terms ship in the box with each unit.
  </p>

  <h2 id="terms">Terms of use</h2>
  <p>
    By visiting this site you agree that the content here is provided as-is,
    for informational purposes. ARCADIA is a tool; medical, legal, or
    survival decisions you make are yours. Always seek qualified professional
    help when one is available.
  </p>
